originalText.text: I called Westside Dental yesterday morning to schedule an emergency appointment after my filling broke. To make room for me, they managed to cram me into their extremely packed schedule.  The front desk employee was incredibly polite and helpful when I arrived. My examination was performed by a fantastic, quick dentist. I'm thrilled that they are my dentist because their dental clinic is a hidden gem on the upper west side, located on 72nd.
